text: Bilal Anwar (born 16 July 1995) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first- class debut for Lahore Whites in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 8 September 2018. He made his List A debut for Lahore Whites in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam One Day Cup on 13 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Lahore Whites cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
